en_7035729_0	Three hundred factory hands at a garment factory in Balangoda were taken ill and hospitalised after suspected food poisoning.
en_7035729_1	According to hospital officials, some 100 were discharged while another 200 are undergoing further medical treatment. Patients said they vomited and fainted while some experienced stomach aches after consuming food provided to them.
en_7035729_2	Hospital sources said that the patients are not in critical condition.
